Lorna McCarthy was stabbed through the heart by her husband Barry McCarthy in September last year . 
  She had feared for her life in the hours leading up to her death after he found out she was using dating websites . 
  The couple had separated four months earlier after 25 years of marriage . 
  McCarthy was found guilty of murder at Norwich Crown Court . 
  He will be sentenced on May 1 after being found guilty by a jury . 
 